CREATE:
POST https://10.1.1.4/mgmt/tm/ltm/rule/

{
    "name": "BlocklistIP_Rule",
    "apiAnonymous": "when FLOW_INIT {\n    if { [class match [IP::remote_addr] equals BlocklistIP_DataGroup]} {\n        log local0. \"Attacker IP [IP::client_addr]\"\n        drop\n    }\n}"
}

READ:
GET: https://10.1.1.4/mgmt/tm/ltm/rule/~Common~BlocklistIP_Rule

UPDATE:
PATCH: https://10.1.1.4/mgmt/tm/ltm/rule/~Common~BlocklistIP_Rule
{
    "apiAnonymous": "when FLOW_INIT {\n    if { [class match [IP::remote_addr] equals BlocklistIP_DataGroup]} {\n        log local0. \"Rejecting IP [IP::client_addr]\"\n        reject\n    }\n}"
}